HERITAGE COMMONS HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION
Annual Calendar

    1.0 This calendar represents anual dates for the community.  It is not a complete list, nor is the board required to scheule all events listed.

    January, Last Weekend:      External Holiday Lighting must be removed
    March,  Last Weekend:       Pool Opens
    April:                      Annual Tree Trimming
    May:                        Annual Roof Cleaning
    August, Last Weekend:       Pool Closes
    August, Last Sunday:        Pool Dog Day (No Humans in Water, pool officially closes after event)
    November, First Weekend:    External Holiday Lighting may be installed

